1
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,199
<b>By the way,</b>

2
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,039
<b>are you Thai?</b>

3
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,639
<b>Yeah, I am.</b>

4
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,360
<b>Then...</b>

5
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,639
<b>how come you speak Thai so well?</b>

6
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,760
<b>My mother is Thai, actually. That's how I learned.</b>

7
00:01:58,679 --> 00:01:59,639
<b>I'm Karn, by the way.</b>

8
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,400
<b>And you are...?</b>

9
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:06,280
<b>Kita. But you can just call me Q.</b>

10
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:11,239
<b>Alright then. This round is on me.</b>

11
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,639
<b>To celebrate us finally meeting.</b>

12
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,719
<b>Thank you.</b>

13
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,880
<b>You're getting a bit tipsy,Q.</b>

14
00:03:15,239 --> 00:03:16,000
<b>Want me to take you home?</b>

15
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:19,920
<b>It’s okay.</b>

16
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,519
<b>I can manage.</b>

17
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,320
<b>Thanks for today.</b>

18
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:36,440
<b>I had a really great time.</b>

19
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,719
<b>I did too.</b>

20
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,199
<b>Let's do this again sometime.</b>

21
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:49,000
<b>See you around.</b>

22
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,280
<b>Sure thing.</b>

23
00:04:40,039 --> 00:04:41,480
<b>(Dad): You've graduated. </b>

24
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,920
<b>It's time to come back to Thailand.</b>

25
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:47,800
<b>(Kita): I want to travel for a bit longer.</b>

26
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,519
<b>(Dad): No. You need to return ASAP.</b>

27
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:53,400
<b>I've already arranged a job for you.</b>

28
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,719
<b>(Kita): Dad, I'm not ready to come back yet.</b>

29
00:05:00,159 --> 00:05:03,039
<b>(Dad): I’m giving you one week to get ready and fly home.</b>

30
00:05:20,119 --> 00:05:23,000
<b>(Karn): Good night :)</b>

31
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,800
<b>Smells amazing. Is it ready yet?</b>

32
00:05:51,239 --> 00:05:52,079
<b>Just finished.</b>

33
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,000
<b>Hurry up!</b>

34
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,360
<b>Here you go.</b>

35
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,119
<b>Put it down right here.</b>

36
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,039
<b>Does it look good?</b>

37
00:05:59,239 --> 00:05:59,840
<b>So good!</b>

38
00:06:01,159 --> 00:06:01,800
<b>Let’s eat.</b>

39
00:06:05,719 --> 00:06:06,440
<b>Now this is what I'm talking about.</b>

40
00:06:07,039 --> 00:06:07,760
<b>Delicious!</b>

41
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,119
<b>I’m so jealous of you.</b>

42
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,360
<b>Your parents actually understand you.</b>

43
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:14,780
<b>Why?</b>

44
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,920
<b>You want to transition like me now?</b>

45
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,559
<b>Shut up! </b>

46
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:25,559
<b>I mean I'm jealous they accept you for who you are.</b>

47
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,000
<b>Look at me.</b>

48
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:32,119
<b>I stepped out of line once and got kicked out.</b>

49
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,519
<b>Oh, there's lemonade in the fridge.</b>

50
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,559
<b>Want some?</b>

51
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,519
<b> I'll get it.</b>

52
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:43,780
<b>Tang,</b>

53
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,519
<b>how many dishes did you make?</b>

54
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,920
<b>What's stressing you out?</b>

55
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,079
<b>So...</b>

56
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,199
<b>what’s your next move?</b>

57
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,380
<b>How about this?</b>

58
00:07:01,119 --> 00:07:04,679
<b>You should just move in here for good.</b>

59
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,719
<b>Seriously!</b>

60
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,199
<b>I won't be lonely,</b>

61
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:11,639
<b>and I get to eat great food every day.</b>

62
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,519
<b>(Phone rings)</b>

63
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:16,920
<b>Is that someone from home?</b>

64
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,699
<b>No,</b>

65
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:18,760
<b> I don't recognize the number.</b>

66
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,199
<b>Give me a sec.</b>

67
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,019
<b>Hello?</b>

68
00:07:31,719 --> 00:07:32,639
<b>Who was that?</b>

69
00:07:33,239 --> 00:07:33,739
<b>It was...</b>

70
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,480
<b>that guy.</b>

71
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,559
<b>Which guy?</b>

72
00:07:38,239 --> 00:07:39,639
<b>The food critic.</b>

73
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,400
<b>He called to apologize.</b>

74
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:47,920
<b>And he said he has some business to discuss.</b>

75
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:49,699
<b>Tell you what,</b>

76
00:07:50,239 --> 00:07:51,159
<b>I'm coming with you.</b>

77
00:07:52,559 --> 00:07:53,199
<b>Stay right there.</b>

78
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,960
<b>Wait, why? Oh,</b>

79
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,119
<b>I see... keeping him all to yourself?</b>

80
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,280
<b>In your dreams.</b>

81
00:08:00,119 --> 00:08:01,400
<b>You’re my best friend.</b>

82
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,920
<b>And because of that,</b>

83
00:08:03,119 --> 00:08:05,880
<b>friends do NOT date people I can't stand.</b>

84
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,599
<b>Got it?</b>

85
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,439
<b>Take a seat.</b>

86
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:22,159
<b>Order whatever you want.</b>

87
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:22,899
<b>No thanks,</b>

88
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,479
<b>I already ate.</b>

89
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,720
<b>Just say what you have to say.</b>

90
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,319
<b>Uh...</b>

91
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:28,880
<b>I...</b>

92
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,020
<b>wait a second.</b>

93
00:08:35,479 --> 00:08:36,359
<b>You really have to record this?</b>

94
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:40,279
<b>It’s for my dad. He needs to know the truth.</b>

95
00:08:41,199 --> 00:08:42,600
<b>Go on. Apologize.</b>

96
00:08:43,239 --> 00:08:43,800
<b>Fine.</b>

97
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,720
<b> I’m sorry. </b>

98
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:47,720
<b>Your dessert was excellent, Nabtang</b>

99
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,920
<b>But... I’m talking about the second time.</b>

100
00:08:55,359 --> 00:08:58,439
<b>Was the first time really that salty?</b>

101
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,039
<b>But why should I believe you?</b>

102
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,960
<b>But why should I believe you?</b>

103
00:09:09,399 --> 00:09:09,899
<b>What is it?</b>

104
00:09:12,239 --> 00:09:13,479
<b>I have my grandfather's restaurant </b>

105
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,119
<b>on Baimai Khram Island.</b>

106
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:18,000
<b>Would you like to be my chef?"</b>

107
00:09:19,239 --> 00:09:20,439
<b>Why me? </b>

108
00:09:21,319 --> 00:09:22,800
<b>You never even believed in my cooking.</b>

109
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:27,079
<b>These are the three conditions set by Mr. Anan.</b>

110
00:09:27,319 --> 00:09:31,039
<b>If you fulfill all three conditions...</b>

111
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:34,239
<b>...you will have full rights to the inheritance.</b>

112
00:09:34,359 --> 00:09:39,840
<b>First: You must run the restaurant for one full year.</b>

113
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:44,239
<b>Second: You must manage the restaurant in person.</b>

114
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:48,840
<b>And finally: Mr. Anan has already specified </b>

115
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,840
<b>the person he wants as the head chef.</b>

116
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,800
<b>This person is...</b>

117
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:07,119
<b>This is weird. Is this a scam? I'm not doing it.</b>

118
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,960
<b>You'll have total creative control over the menu.</b>

119
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,319
<b>And?</b>

120
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,880
<b>Anything else?</b>

121
00:10:20,079 --> 00:10:21,800
<b>Because it still sounds pretty boring.</b>

122
00:10:23,079 --> 00:10:24,039
<b>If you complete the year,</b>

123
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:28,600
<b>I’ll give you a five-million-baht bonus.</b>

124
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:33,239
<b>When do you need an answer?</b>

125
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,600
<b>As soon as possible.</b>

126
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,119
<b>Can I ask you something?</b>

127
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,399
<b>Why the sunglasses indoors?</b>

128
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,479
<b>It's a style choice.</b>

129
00:10:46,239 --> 00:10:47,560
<b>One step away from being a lottery seller.</b>

130
00:10:48,079 --> 00:10:50,199
<b>And the prize goes to... </b>

131
00:11:10,479 --> 00:11:11,640
<b>You're actually kind of cute, you know.</b>

132
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,159
<b>You just need to look longer.</b>

133
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,239
<b>Give this a try.</b>

134
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,279
<b>Let me know if you like it.</b>

135
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:29,840
<b>I'm leaving now.</b>

136
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,319
<b>I'll take two chicken legs, please.</b>

137
00:11:48,359 --> 00:11:48,859
<b>Sure thing.</b>

138
00:12:15,439 --> 00:12:16,600
<b>This is amazing!</b>

139
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,960
<b>What kind of chicken is this?</b>

140
00:12:20,319 --> 00:12:21,760
<b>I've never tasted anything like it.</b>

141
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:25,760
<b>It's definitely not Hat Yai fried chicken.</b>

142
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:29,079
<b>"This is Ma-khwaen fried chicken.</b>

143
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:31,239
<b> It’s a specialty from Nan.</b>

144
00:12:34,199 --> 00:12:37,479
<b>You don't look Thai at all.</b>

145
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:40,239
<b>How is your Thai so clear?</b>

146
00:12:41,199 --> 00:12:43,359
<b>I'm mixed—half Korean, actually.</b>

147
00:12:44,199 --> 00:12:46,359
<b>But I've lived in Thailand for years now.</b>

148
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,479
<b>It's my first time here,</b>

149
00:12:51,439 --> 00:12:53,680
<b>though. Enjoy your trip!</b>

150
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,039
<b>I'm actually here for work.</b>

151
00:12:57,439 --> 00:12:59,960
<b>But if I'm free, I'll visit often.</b>

152
00:13:01,239 --> 00:13:02,039
<b>It's so good!</b>

153
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:04,560
<b> You're very welcome.</b>

154
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,020
<b>Yes, boss.</b>

155
00:13:24,239 --> 00:13:25,600
<b>Regarding the signature menu... </b>

156
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:26,899
<b>I've got it.</b>

157
00:13:28,439 --> 00:13:30,560
<b>Just let me tweak the recipe a bit, </b>

158
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,319
<b>then I'll let you taste it.</b>

159
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:34,000
<b>yes</b>

160
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:53,439
<b>Khao Khluk Kapi Bibimbap</b>

161
00:13:56,159 --> 00:13:58,640
<b>Are you just going to stare, or are you going to try some?</b>

162
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,520
<b>Looking for someone?</b>

163
00:15:24,359 --> 00:15:27,960
<b>No. I just came to order a drink.</b>

164
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:31,840
<b>Wait a sec. I have a new drink for you to try.</b>

165
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,560
<b>Feel free to criticize.</b>

166
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,560
<b>How is it?</b>

167
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,239
<b>It's delicious.</b>

168
00:16:12,319 --> 00:16:14,680
<b>But... it's got quite a kick.</b>

169
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:19,239
<b>Just like you. </b>

170
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:23,119
<b>Sweet, beautiful...</b>

171
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:25,319
<b>but with a hidden spice.</b>

172
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,119
<b>You even know the word 'Zapp'?</b>

173
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:31,520
<b>Of course. </b>

174
00:16:41,119 --> 00:16:44,359
<b>Is something wrong, Q? You look sad.</b>

175
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,880
<b>My dad is forcing me to go back to Thailand.</b>

176
00:17:06,199 --> 00:17:08,840
<b>I don't want to go. </b>

177
00:17:13,439 --> 00:17:15,680
<b>I’m so happy here, Karn.</b>

178
00:17:18,199 --> 00:17:21,800
<b>I’m free here. I can be whoever I want to be.</b>

179
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,640
<b>When do you leave?</b>

180
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:29,520
<b> In about two or three days.</b>

181
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:33,760
<b>That’s so soon. </b>

182
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:40,880
<b>I’m going to miss you, Q.</b>

183
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,439
<b>I’ll miss you too.</b>

184
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,560
<b>This is really good.</b>

185
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:16,039
<b>Want one?</b>

186
00:18:16,039 --> 00:18:16,960
<b>no</b>

187
00:18:17,159 --> 00:18:17,800
<b>give it a try.</b>

188
00:18:18,159 --> 00:18:19,079
<b>no</b>

189
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:29,800
<b>How about this one?</b>

190
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:28,600
<b>I'm sorry I didn't tell you sooner...</b>

191
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,560
<b>that I'm a chef.</b>

192
00:19:40,479 --> 00:19:41,079
<b>Karn...</b>

193
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:43,560
<b>will you be with me?</b>

194
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,840
<b>My mother is gone.</b>

195
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:05,079
<b>Hiring two chefs.</b>

196
00:20:06,079 --> 00:20:07,079
<b>"I want to work here.</b>

197
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:13,079
<b>I made a promise to someone.</b>

198
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,159
<b>And I really liked this island.</b>

199
00:20:16,239 --> 00:20:19,680
<b>You really do look like a thug, </b>

200
00:20:20,399 --> 00:20:21,600
<b>don't you? For a market owner."</b>

201
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:25,680
<b>I like your feistiness.</b>

202
00:20:27,279 --> 00:20:27,779
<b>It’s hot.</b>
